    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Your website platform determines how well AI can read, understand and cite your content. Some platforms produce clean HTML that AI crawlers love. Others generate JavaScript-heavy code that AI cannot parse at all.</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">This is not about which platform looks best. It is about which platforms produce websites that AI search engines can actually work with.</p>

