      <details class="border border-border rounded-lg p-5">
        <summary class="font-semibold text-heading cursor-pointer">Can I make any website AI-ready?</summary>
        <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">To a degree. You can improve AI readiness on any platform by adding schema, allowing AI crawlers, and structuring content well. But some platforms have fundamental limitations in their code output that cannot be fixed.</p>
